member.example:
This sample shows how to call DummyOperationAsync.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
JsonMergePatchClient client = new JsonMergePatchClient(endpoint);

Response response = await client.DummyOperationAsync();

Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

This sample shows how to call DummyOperationAsync with all request content.

Uri endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
JsonMergePatchClient client = new JsonMergePatchClient(endpoint);

Response response = await client.DummyOperationAsync();

Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

